Grafana:

1) Connect to aks cluster : 

az account set --subscription 92a23ff9-4506-4981-af48-d0832ba7eb21

az aks get-credentials --resource-group AKStask --name aks001

2) kubectl create namespace monitoring 

3) kubectl create -f grafana-datasource-config.yaml

4) kubectl create -f deployment.yaml 

5) kubectl create -f  service.yaml

6) kubectl get po -n monitoring

7) kubectl port-forward -n monitoring grafana-64c89f57f7-v9974 3000 &

App:

1) az acr login --name acr001task

1.1)  az aks update -n aks001 -g AKStask --attach-acr acr001task

2) sudo docker push acr001task.azurecr.io/azure-vote-front:v1

3) kubectl apply -f azure-vote-all-in-one-redis.yaml

4) kubectl get service azure-vote-front --watch
